.0, "block": 29, "par": 1, "line": 1, "i": 156}, {"text": "e", "x": 238, "y": 2355, "w": 13, "h": 14, "conf": 69.0, "block": 29, "par": 1, "line": 1, "i": 157}, {"text": "trente-six", "x": 263, "y": 2347, "w": 154, "h": 28, "conf": 90.0, "block": 29, "par": 1, "line": 1, "i": 158}], "sentences": [{"id": 0, "text": "LE CORPS - LES MOUVEMENTS", "words": [0, 1, 2, 3, 4]}, {"id": 1, "text": "LE MOUVEMENT ?", "words": [5, 6, 7]}, {"id": 2, "text": "LA POSTURE", "words": [8, 9]}, {"id": 3, "text": "e s'asseoir — être assis(e) — Asseyez-vous !", "words": [10, 11, 12, 13, 14, 15, 16, 17]}, {"id": 4, "text": "(Assieds-toi!)", "words": [18]}, {"id": 5, "text": "Je suis assis sur une", "words": [19, 20, 21, 22, 23]}, {"id": 6, "text": "- D'accord, je m'assieds sur une chaise.", "words": [24, 25, 26, 27, 28, 29, 30]}, {"id": 7, "text": "— Elle est assise.", "words": [31, 32, 33, 34]}, {"id": 8, "text": "se lever — être debout - Levez-vous !", "words": [35, 36, 37, 38, 39, 40, 41, 42]}, {"id": 9, "text": "(Lève-toi!)", "words": [43]}, {"id": 10, "text": "- Je suis debout.", "words": [44, 45, 46, 47]}, {"id": 11, "text": "2 = - D'accord, je me lève.", "words": [48, 49, 50, 51, 52, 53, 54]}, {"id": 12, "text": "(invariable) L 1", "words": [55, 56, 57]}, {"id": 13, "text": "A tre © — £ à 2, : D) Bastien tient un ballon dans Manon court et attrape le ballon, mais après, Maxime porte un sac", "words": [58, 59, 60, 61, 62, 63, 64, 65, 66, 67, 68, 69, 70, 71, 72, 73, 74, 75, 76, 77, 78, 79, 80, 81, 82, 83]}, {"id": 14, "text": "les mains, puis il lance le ballon.", "words": [84, 85, 86, 87, 88, 89, 90]}, {"id": 15, "text": "elle tombe.", "words": [91, 92]}, {"id": 16, "text": "très lourd.", "words": [93, 94]}, {"id": 17, "text": "BIJOUTERIE", "words": [95]}, {"id": 18, "text": "F5 AA 1 DÉS Mathilde pose (= met) le livre sur la table; Joël marche dans la rue; Joël sort du magasin.", "words": [96, 97, 98, 99, 100, 101, 102, 103, 104, 105, 106, 107, 108, 109, 110, 111, 112, 113, 114, 115, 116, 117]}, {"id": 19, "text": "Julien enlève le livre de la table.", "words": [118, 119, 120, 121, 122, 123, 124]}, {"id": 20, "text": "il entre dans le magasin.", "words": [125, 126, 127, 128, 129]}, {"id": 21, "text": "Louis apporte du champagne.", "words": [130, 131, 132, 133]}, {"id": 22, "text": "Nadège emmène les enfants au cinéma.", "words": [134, 135, 136, 137, 138, 139]}, {"id": 23, "text": "«Glaces à emporter»", "words": [140, 141, 142]}, {"id": 24, "text": "Remarque : On «emmène » une personne, mais on «emporte » quelque chose.", "words": [143, 144, 145, 146, 147, 148, 149, 150, 151, 152, 153, 154, 155]}, {"id": 25, "text": "36 e trente-six", "words": [156, 157, 158]}]}